title: JVP protestors occupy one lane of High Level road
body_lines: One lane of the High Level road up to Police Park has been blocked due to a protest march by the members of the Janatha Vimukthi Peramuna (JVP).
The JVP held a three-day anti-government protest march from Beruwala demanding President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and his government to step down.
The protest march is to reach the Lipton Circus in Colombo today
